    GET READY FOR A WILDE ADVENTURE!

    CAT WILDE IN THE ECLIPSE OF THE SUN GOD

    Get ready for a Wilde adventure!

    ABOUT GAME

    Cat Wilde in the Eclipse of the Sun God is a 5x3 cascading video slot game, with 20 fixed paylines, featuring a win multiplier on cascade wins, and a FREE SPINS feature.


    Winning symbols are removed, and new symbols fill up the reel. Cascades continue until no more wins can be created. Win multiplier raises on cascades! Win multiplier can increment up to x10 in the base game, and up to x70 during FREE SPINS!


    The Moon Goddess symbol is the SCATTER. 3 SCATTERS landing on reel 1, 3 and 5 trigger 10 initial FREE SPINS. SCATTERS act as WILDS in FREE SPINS! During FREE SPINS, collect 5 Moon Goddess SCATTERS for an additional 5 spins (up to a maximum of 40), and upgrade the multiplier win values.


    The Sun God symbol is the WILD. WILDS can land on reels 2, 3 and 4, during Main Game and they substitute for all symbols, except SCATTERS. Wilds land anywhere during FREE SPINS.
